‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ {subfolder}/
‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ README.md           # Subfolder details (classes/interfaces)
```

### No Duplication Rule

**FORBIDDEN:**
- ‚ùå Copying class documentation from subfolder README to library README
- ‚ùå Duplicating interface details in multiple READMEs
- ‚ùå Repeating usage examples at multiple levels

**REQUIRED:**
- ‚úÖ Index READMEs contain overview and links only
- ‚úÖ Detailed READMEs contain full class/interface documentation
- ‚úÖ Links point to detailed READMEs for specifics

### Link Requirements

**All Links Must:**
- Use relative paths (e.g., `../README.md`, `Providers/README.md`)
- Point to existing files
- Be verified before committing
- Follow consistent naming

**Link Format:**
```markdown
- [{Library Name}]({library}/README.md) - {Brief description}
- [{Subfolder Name}]({subfolder}/README.md) - {Brief description}
```

